- Raspberry Pi 4 uses BCM2711 Broadcom chip.
(https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/hardware/raspberrypi/bcm2711/README.md)
- BCM2711 ARM Peripherals Manul
(https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/hardware/raspberrypi/bcm2711/rpi_DATA_2711_1p0.pdf)
- Raspberry Pi 4 reserved memory above address 0x4_7C00_0000 for devices.
(BCM2711 Page 14)

